/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-03.md:30:- The chain says "full conjugate completion," which is necessary but not sufficient. The real burden is exact closure under all forced interactions, not just mirror completion. Once that is imposed honestly, the "small family" may stop being small.
