+- Exact criterion:
+
+  ```text
+  Fix thresholds
+
+    0 < theta_B < theta_C < theta_D < theta_E <= 1,
+    Lambda_itin in (0,1),
+    kappa_rot > 1,
+
+  together with the canonical amplitude anchor |A_n(0)| = 1
+  and canonical phase anchor arg A_n(0) = 0.
