+- Exact criterion:
+
+  ```text
+  Let
+
+    D_on(t)
+      := |Q_clk(t)| + |Q_seed(t)| + |Q_amp(t)|
+         + |Q_rot^A(t)| + |Q_rot^D(t)| + |Q_next(t)|.
+
+  Partition the forced off-template channels into
